This project is a simple College Management App Wireframe developed as part of a UI/UX design task. The wireframe demonstrates the basic structure and navigation flow of a mobile application designed for students and educational institutions.
Features
Student Login Screen
Dashboard Screen
Attendance Tracking
Assignment Management
Exam Schedule
Fee Payment Section
Student Profile Screen
Purpose
The main objective of this project is to design a user-friendly mobile application interface that helps students manage their academic activities efficiently.
